headline: What Recent Earnings Mean for First Solar’s Stock Price in 2025
summary: If you are considering what to do with First Solar stock right now, you are far from alone. The shares have had a remarkable run over the past few years, climbing a staggering 168.4% in the past five years and 83.1% over three. Even more recently, the stock is up 21.2% year-to-date, though it dipped slightly in the past week, dropping 1.8%. These moves have not happened in isolation.
